## ⚙️ 2. TECH STACK & DEPENDENCIES (STRICT)
**Install ONLY these:**
```bash
npm create astro@latest -- --template minimal
npm install @astrojs/tailwind astro-seo
npm install -D @astrojs/sitemap
```
- **NO** React/Vue/Svelte components
- **NO** client-side JS frameworks
- **NO** heavy UI libraries (shadcn, DaisyUI, etc.)
- **NO** external CDNs for fonts/scripts (self-host or use system fonts)
- Use Astro's built-in `<Image>`, `<Video>`, and partial hydration (`client:load` only if strictly necessary)

---

## 🧱 3. CORE PAGES & COMPONENT SPECS

### 🔹 `BaseLayout.astro`
- Includes `<Seo>` component (dynamic title, meta, OG, JSON-LD)
- Loads Tailwind via `@astrojs/tailwind`
- Injects `<EventTracking>` in `<head>`
- System font stack: `font-sans: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif`
- `scroll-behavior: smooth`, `color-scheme: light`

### 🔹 `Header.astro` & `Footer.astro`
- Sticky header, transparent on hero, solid on scroll
- Nav: `Products | Compliance | About | 📞 Book Call`
- Footer: Quick links, certifications list, contact email, copyright
- Mobile: Hamburger menu (pure CSS, zero JS)

### 🔹 `Hero.astro` (Homepage)
- H1: `"Reliable Psyllium Husk Supply for US/EU Formulators"`
- Sub: `"Certified • Traceable • Scalable. Book a 15-min sourcing call."`
- Dual CTAs: 
  - Primary: `📞 Book Your Sourcing Call` → scrolls to `#book` (Calendly embed)
  - Secondary: `📥 Download Import Playbook` → links to `/resources/playbook`
- Trust badges row: `USDA Organic | EU Certified | FDA Registered | FSSAI | HALAL | KOSHER`
- Background: `<video>` muted, autoplay, loop, playsinline, `<2MB`, opacity 20%

### 🔹 `SpecBuilder.astro` (MVP)
```html
<form name="spec-builder" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" class="space-y-4">
  <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="spec-builder" />
  <p hidden><label>Bot: <input name="bot-field" /></label></p>
  
  <label>Grade
    <select name="grade" required>
      <option value="95">95% Purity</option>
      <option value="98">98% Purity</option>
      <option value="99">99% Purity</option>
    </select>
  </label>
  
  <label>Mesh Size
    <input type="range" name="mesh" min="20" max="100" step="20" value="80" />
    <span id="mesh-display">80 mesh</span>
  </label>
  
  <label>Packaging
    <select name="packaging">
      <option value="25kg">25kg Bags</option>
      <option value="10kg">10kg Bags</option>
      <option value="500kg">500kg Jumbo</option>
    </select>
  </label>
  
  <input type="hidden" name="referrer" value="homepage" />
  <button type="submit" class="bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 text-white px-5 py-2 rounded font-semibold w-full">
    Get Spec Summary & Book Call →
  </button>
</form>

<script>
  // Update mesh display on slider change
  const slider = document.querySelector('input[name="mesh"]');
  const display = document.getElementById('mesh-display');
  slider.addEventListener('input', () => display.textContent = `${slider.value} mesh`);

  // Netlify form submit → redirect to Calendly with params
  const form = document.querySelector('form[name="spec-builder"]');
  form.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    const formData = new FormData(form);
    const grade = formData.get('grade');
    const mesh = formData.get('mesh');
    const pack = formData.get('packaging');
    const params = new URLSearchParams({ grade, mesh, pack }).toString();
    
    // Submit to Netlify via fetch
    fetch('/', {
      method: 'POST',
      headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded' },
      body: new URLSearchParams(formData).toString()
    }).then(() => {
      window.location.href = `https://calendly.com/your-link/sourcing-call?${params}`;
    });
  });
</script>
```

### 🔹 `resources/playbook.astro` (Gated)
- Preview section (3 pages blurred/low-res)
- Netlify form: `name`, `company`, `email`, `country`, `application`
- On submit → redirect to `/thank-you?guide=playbook`
- `/thank-you.astro` auto-triggers PDF download from `/public/playbook-rm-psyllium.pdf`

### 🔹 `CalendlyEmbed.astro`
```html
<div class="calendly-inline-widget" data-url="https://calendly.com/your-link/sourcing-call" style="min-width:320px;height:630px;"></div>
<script src="https://assets.calendly.com/assets/external/widget.js" async></script>
```
- Add `onEventScheduled` listener to fire `gtag('event', 'calendly_booked')`

---

## 🔌 4. INTEGRATIONS & DATA FLOW

| Feature | Implementation |
|---------|---------------|
| **Netlify Forms** | `data-netlify="true"`, honeypot, `netlify-honeypot="bot-field"`, success redirect |
| **Calendly Params** | Pass `?grade=X&mesh=Y&pack=Z` via URL. Pre-fill Calendly custom questions using JS if API allows, else log in CRM |
| **SEO/JSON-LD** | Use `astro-seo` or manual `<script type="application/ld+json">` with `@type: "Organization"` + `Product` schema |
| **Analytics** | Plausible/GA4 snippet in `<head>`. Track: `form_submit`, `calendly_booked`, `guide_download` |
| **Redirects** | `netlify.toml`: `[[redirects]] from = "/playbook" to = "/resources/playbook" status = 301` |

---

## ⚡ 5. PERFORMANCE, SEO & SECURITY RULES (NON-NEGOTIABLE)
- ✅ **Lighthouse Target:** Performance ≥95, Accessibility ≥95, Best Practices ≥95, SEO ≥95
- ✅ **Images:** Use `<Image>` component, explicit `width`/`height`, `loading="lazy"`, `decoding="async"`, serve WebP/AVIF
- ✅ **Fonts:** Self-host or use system stack. No Google Fonts CDN
- ✅ **CLS:** Zero layout shift. Reserve space for all media/forms
- ✅ **JavaScript:** <50KB total. No blocking scripts. Defer/async all external
- ✅ **Security:** CSP header via `_headers` file, honeypot on all forms, no inline `eval()`
- ✅ **Accessibility:** `aria-labels`, focus states, contrast ≥4.5:1, semantic HTML5

---

## 🧪 6. TESTING & VALIDATION PROTOCOL
Before marking complete, run and confirm:
```bash
1. npm run build → zero errors
2. npx astro preview → forms submit, Calendly loads, redirect works
3. Lighthouse CLI → all scores ≥90 (target 95)
4. Form Test → submit spec-builder → check Netlify dashboard → verify Calendly redirect with params
5. Mobile Test → iOS Safari + Chrome DevTools → no overflow, tap targets ≥44px
6. SEO Check → valid OG tags, JSON-LD, hreflang (if any), sitemap.xml generated
7. Console → zero warnings, zero CORS errors
```

