## 🚀 7. DEPLOYMENT & CI/CD
1. Push to GitHub `main` branch
2. Connect to Netlify (auto-deploy on push)
3. Add custom domain via Netlify DNS or external registrar
4. Enable: HTTPS, HSTS, Brotli compression, Asset optimization
5. Add `_headers`:
   ```
   /*
     Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
     X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
     Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
   ```
6. Add `_redirects`:
   ```
   /playbook /resources/playbook 301
   /book https://calendly.com/your-link 302
   /* /404 404
   ```

