## 🚫 8. STRICT CONSTRAINTS (WHAT NOT TO DO)
- ❌ Do NOT add React/Vue/Svelte
- ❌ Do NOT use Tailwind plugins or custom CSS files unless absolutely necessary
- ❌ Do NOT hardcode Calendly links without param-passing logic
- ❌ Do NOT use client-side routing for form redirects
- ❌ Do NOT exceed 50KB JS total
- ❌ Do NOT skip honeypot or form validation
- ❌ Do NOT use stock photos. Use placeholders with `alt="Factory walkthrough"` until media is replaced
- ❌ Do NOT add comments like `// TODO` in production code

